{"tid":99462,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩Battle Spirits","createTime":"2017-01-29T08:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T07:05:43.000Z","uid":75845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a299124f3d99129f7bfa3153269c8d218203e88","tid":99462,"uid":75845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"真毒巴好似無轉台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e3975a621833d3537be81cf5a2924a07bc5988","tid":99462,"uid":75845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"香港官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.battlespirits.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.battlespirits.com&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a47ec369\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.battlespirits.com</a><br />\n<br />\n有心人嘅blog，卡效齊過同準過官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://00cardlist.blog.fc2.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00cardlist.blog.fc2.com&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=fa4385e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://00cardlist.blog.fc2.com</a>"},{"pid":"34e86bc538610c29a191017c52e7209d8e69caaa","tid":99462,"uid":75845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">BS39-X06 戌の十二神皇グリードッグ　7(藍3綠2)神皇・異合　&lt;1&gt;Lv1 11000　&lt;2&gt;Lv2 15000　&lt;4&gt;Lv3 21000 藍<br />\nLv1・Lv2・Lv3《封印》『這張Spirit攻擊時』<br />\n這張Spirit上的[魂Core]放置在自己生命值區。<br />\n《封印時》Lv1・Lv2・Lv3【強奪】『這張Spirit攻擊/防禦時』<br />\n觀看對手全部手牌，須捨棄當中1張Magic卡。該Magic卡的主要/Flash效果，自己不支付Cost立即可以發揮。<br />\nLv3『互相的攻擊階段』<br />\n一個回合最多3次，對手手牌減少時，回復自己1張持有系統：「神皇」/「十冠」的Spirit。</span><br />\n<br />\n癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 強奪個效好過分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c16893629174c50dd31f07d74328aec3109151b","tid":99462,"uid":15050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:50:54.000Z","msg":"玩到風霸連環拳果幾代就停咗"},{"pid":"c04a95cb9dd9678bf0a85fe09667286b070c395d","tid":99462,"uid":3095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"玩完十二星座就無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979c7d466c8d77e41a032e3a81adb8f27e6151b2","tid":99462,"uid":84768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:44:41.000Z","msg":"仲玩緊"},{"pid":"711a9e715636433b6abd1ba0a1de7694c3d62e6c","tid":99462,"uid":1304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"回坑留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300ab4277228cec1f9f7174df6db321a6f611972","tid":99462,"uid":18535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回坑留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無師兄帶入坑"},{"pid":"151f745892d9663627a02dba981a092ffe5c01b2","tid":99462,"uid":93215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"真心唔建議回坑，尐卡貴到PK(散收)，又出勁多新野要重新學會好煩。"},{"pid":"7c8789ffb49ef31b947ef2f8d5fd24c41d850949","tid":99462,"uid":88008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"遊戲王正d"},{"pid":"e31ca14220334d366d750494ea994d7b43326750","tid":99462,"uid":88601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.battlespirits.com/mydeck/decksrc/201810/1538384764.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.battlespirits.com%2Fmydeck%2Fdecksrc%2F201810%2F1538384764.html&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3f8ed482\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.battlespirits.com/mydeck/decksrc/201810/15383847